| **CEO** | **Xavier Rossinyol** | ex gategroup; guida l’integrazione retail-F&B.  ([Avolta's Leadership | Avolta](https://www.avoltaworld.com/en/meet-avolta/our-leadership)) |
| **Lead Independent Director** | **Heekyung Jo Min** | corporate governance & sustainability.  ([Avolta's Leadership | Avolta](https://www.avoltaworld.com/en/meet-avolta/our-leadership)) |
| **CFO** | **Yves Gerster** | in carica dal 2019.  ([Avolta's Leadership | Avolta](https://www.avoltaworld.com/en/meet-avolta/our-leadership)) |

* Il CdA conta 11 membri; >⅔ indipendenti; tre comitati: Audit, Remuneration, Nomination & Sustainability.  
* **Azionariato:** Edizione Holding 22,17 % (31 dic 2024); poi Advent Intl. 7,3 %, Richemont 5 %, Qatar Holding 4,5 % ecc.  ([Our Investors - Avolta](https://www.avoltaworld.com/en/company/our-stakeholders/investors?utm_source=chatgpt.com))  

